                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Written in Amharic.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#106ra">Fols. 106ra</locus>-rb (below the text): Record concerning a transaction. <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 106ra: በ፲፱፻፴፰ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ወርኁ፡ መጋቢት፡ ዕለቱ፡ ፯ቀን፡ የአዲ፡ ስቡሐ፡ ሽማግሎች፡ ለማርያም፡ ጽዮን፡…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The transaction took place between the people of ʾAddi Sǝbuḥ and Maryam Ṣǝyon.
The date mentioned is 1938 year of mercy (= 1945/46 A.D.)
Written in Amharic; “signed” with numerous finger prints.
                        </item>
